---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="PHCDevworks"
  description="No images. No animations. No nonsense. Just text and links. This is PHCDevworks."
>
  <section class="sp-container sp-py-20 sp-space-y-16 sp-max-w-4xl">
    <article class="sp-space-y-6">
      <h1 class="sp-text-display sp-leading-tight sp-text-6xl">PHCDevworks</h1>
      <p class="sp-text-2xl sp-leading-relaxed">
        No images. No animations. No nonsense.<br />
        Just text and links.
      </p>
      <p class="sp-text-xl sp-text-muted sp-leading-relaxed">
        We build design systems, UI tooling, and developer infrastructure.
        Everything is open source. Everything is on GitHub.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="sp-space-y-8 sp-border-t sp-border-muted sp-pt-12">
      <h2 class="sp-text-3xl sp-font-semibold">What We Build</h2>

      <div class="sp-space-y-6">
        <div>
          <h3 class="sp-text-xl sp-font-semibold sp-mb-2">
            <a
              href="https://github.com/phcdevworks/spectre-tokens"
              class="sp-underline sp-text-accent hover:sp-no-underline"
            >
              Spectre Tokens
            </a>
          </h3>
          <p class="sp-text-muted sp-leading-relaxed">
            Design tokens that define the visual language. JSON, JS/TS, CSS
            variables, and Tailwind outputs. One source of truth for every
            surface.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="sp-text-xl sp-font-semibold sp-mb-2">
            <a
              href="https://github.com/phcdevworks/spectre-ui"
              class="sp-underline sp-text-accent hover:sp-no-underline"
            >
              Spectre UI
            </a>
          </h3>
          <p class="sp-text-muted sp-leading-relaxed">
            Core styling layer. Consumes tokens, ships CSS. Base styles,
            components, utilities, and recipe helpers. No framework lock-in.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="sp-text-xl sp-font-semibold sp-mb-2">
            <a
              href="https://github.com/phcdevworks/spectre-ui-astro"
              class="sp-underline sp-text-accent hover:sp-no-underline"
            >
              Spectre UI Astro
            </a>
          </h3>
          <p class="sp-text-muted sp-leading-relaxed">
            Astro integration. Typed components that map to Spectre UI classes.
            No duplicated logic. No style bloat.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="sp-text-xl sp-font-semibold sp-mb-2">
            <a
              href="https://github.com/phcdevworks/spectre-icons"
              class="sp-underline sp-text-accent hover:sp-no-underline"
            >
              Spectre Icons
            </a>
          </h3>
          <p class="sp-text-muted sp-leading-relaxed">
            Icon system tuned to Spectre spacing, stroke, and typography scales.
            Product-ready, no fuss.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="sp-space-y-6 sp-border-t sp-border-muted sp-pt-12">
      <h2 class="sp-text-3xl sp-font-semibold">Philosophy</h2>
      <div class="sp-space-y-4 sp-text-lg sp-leading-relaxed">
        <p>Design tokens once. Use everywhere. No copy-paste. No drift.</p>
        <p>
          CSS that consumes tokens. Components that consume CSS. Clean layers.
          Clear dependencies.
        </p>
        <p>
          Open source. No vendor lock. Build what you need. Modify what you
          want.
        </p>
        <p>
          This website proves the point: great design doesn't need decoration.
          It needs clarity.
        </p>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="sp-space-y-6 sp-border-t sp-border-muted sp-pt-12">
      <h2 class="sp-text-3xl sp-font-semibold">Links</h2>
      <div class="sp-space-y-2 sp-text-lg">
        <p>
          <a
            href="https://github.com/phcdevworks"
            class="sp-underline sp-text-accent hover:sp-no-underline"
          >
            github.com/phcdevworks
          </a>
        </p>
        <p class="sp-text-muted">
          All repos. All docs. All roadmaps. Everything lives on GitHub.
        </p>
      </div>
    </article>

    <footer
      class="sp-border-t sp-border-muted sp-pt-12 sp-text-muted sp-text-sm"
    >
      <p>
        Â© 2025 PHCDevworks. Text-only by design. No tracking. No analytics. No
        cookies.
      </p>
    </footer>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
